---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Banner from "../../assets/high-tide-aviation-team-of-cfis.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Intro from "../../assets/female-cfis-at-high-tide-aviation.jpg";
import CounterCard from "../../components/CounterCard";
import { stats } from "../../data/stats";
import TopView from "../../assets/top-view.jpg";
import Team from "../../assets/high-tide-aviation-team-southport.jpg";
import StudentSupport from "../../assets/student-support.jpg";
---

<BaseLayout
  siteTitle="Our Story & Team"
  siteDescription="Meet the dedicated team of professionals at High Tide Aviation in Southport, NC. Our experienced pilots and instructors are committed to providing top-notch flight training."
  siteKeywords="High Tide Aviation team, flight instructors Southport NC, aviation professionals Southeast Coast, experienced pilots High Tide, aviation staff Southport NC."
>
  <Header
    slot="header"
    image={Banner}
    title="Get to Know High Tide Aviation"
    alt="High Tide Aviation team of CFIs"
  />

  <section class="py-24 px-5">
    <div
      class="max-w-xl gap-10 lg:max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:gap-20"
    >
      <div class="flex-1 relative">
        <Image
          class="pr-6"
          src={Intro}
          alt="Female CFIs at High Tide Aviation"
        />
        <div
          class="h-3/4 bg-mustard-yellow absolute -z-10 -right-0 w-20 top-[12.5%]"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
        <h2 class="uppercase text-medium-blue font-bold tracking-widest">
          About High Tide Aviation
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-5xl text-dark-blue font-bold leading-tight">
          The High Tide Story
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mt-3 mb-2">
          High Tide Aviation began in 2013 as High Tide Helicopters with just
          one Robinson R22. Quickly expanding to include airplanes, the school
          rebranded and now operates 12 aircraft at locations in Southport, NC,
          and St Simons Island, GA. As the top flight school in Southeastern
          North Carolina and Southeastern Georgia, High Tide offers training for
          commercial licenses and instrument ratings, using ASA publications and
          maintaining a pilot shop.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">
          The company emphasizes community involvement and education, partnering
          with local colleges to teach aviation courses and engaging with local
          youth about aviation careers. High Tide ensures personalized support
          for each student through dedicated specialists, focusing on safety,
          professionalism, and inclusivity. Aspiring pilots are invited to
          explore the coastlines and learn at a leading school known for quality
          training and community commitment.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-5">
          <a href="#the-team" class="btn-blue"> Meet the Team </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-5 scroll-my-20 bg-medium-blue/10">
    <div
      class="max-w-xl gap-10 lg:max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:gap-10"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
        <h2 class="uppercase text-medium-blue font-bold tracking-widest">
          Student Support Specialist
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-5xl text-dark-blue font-bold leading-tight">
          Personalized Guidance at High Tide
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mt-5">
          As such a specialized skill, flight training can be confusing on even
          its best day. We understand that each student comes to us with
          different learning preferences and a diverse range of experiences. To
          better support our students, we have an in-house Student Support
          Department and assign a specific support specialist to every High Tide
          student in Southport and St Simons Island.
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium mb-5 mt-2 text-gray-600">
          Contact us today and receive tailored flight instruction at High Tide
          Aviation.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-5">
          <a href="/contact-us" class="btn-blue"> Contact Us </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <Image
          src={StudentSupport}
          alt="Student getting ready to fly"
          class="object-cover top-0 left-0 -z-10 max-h-96"
          quality={10}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="text-white mx-auto grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
    {
      stats.map((stat) => (
        <CounterCard
          client:only="react"
          icon={stat.icon}
          value={stat.value}
          title={stat.title}
        />
      ))
    }
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-5 scroll-my-20" id="the-team">
    <div
      class="max-w-xl gap-10 lg:max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center lg:gap-20"
    >
      <div class="flex-1 relative">
        <Image class="pr-6" src={Team} alt="High Tide Aviation team" />
        <div
          class="h-3/4 bg-mustard-yellow absolute -z-10 -right-0 w-20 top-[12.5%]"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
        <h2 class="uppercase text-medium-blue font-bold tracking-widest">
          Our elite instruction team
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-5xl text-dark-blue font-bold leading-tight">
          Meet the High Tide Family
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mt-3 mb-2">
          At High Tide Aviation, we pride ourselves on having a highly skilled
          and passionate team of aviation professionals. Our instructors hold a
          diverse range of certifications, including CFI (Certified Flight
          Instructor), CFII (Certified Flight Instructor - Instrument), and MEI
          (Multi-Engine Instructor), ensuring that we can offer a wide array of
          training services tailored to your needs. Whether you are just
          starting out on your aviation journey or looking to advance your
          skills, our team is here to guide you every step of the way.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">
          We invite you to visit us and meet our team in person at our two
          locations in Southport, NC, and St Simons Island, GA. Each location
          offers a unique atmosphere and a variety of training opportunities to
          enhance your flying experience. Reach out to us today to schedule your
          visit and take the first step towards reaching new heights with High
          Tide Aviation!
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-5">
          <a href="/contact-us" class="btn-blue"> Visit High Tide </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

