  <section class="bg-medium-blue/10">
    <section class="py-24 px-5">
      <div
        class="max-w-xl gap-10 lg:max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center lg:gap-20"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
          <h2 class="uppercase text-medium-blue font-bold tracking-widest">
            Our Culture
          </h2>
          <h3 class="text-5xl text-dark-blue font-bold leading-tight">
            Student Life at High Tide Aviation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            Pilot training at High Tide Aviation is much more than flight
            lessons and logging hours. We strive to make your time as a student
            an experience in becoming part of a larger community. It's important
            to us that you feel at home when learning with us.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium mb-5 mt-2 text-gray-600">
            Check out Ella's story and understand why our students choose to be
            a part of the High Tide family.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-5">
            <a href="/enrollment-form" class="btn-blue"> Enroll Now </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 w-full">
          <div
            style="height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 56.25%; position: relative; width: 100%;"
          >
            <iframe
              style="position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;"
              src="https://tube.rvere.com/embed?v=v5Hn5bCrzlg"
              title="YouTube video player"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
              allowfullscreen
            >
            </iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section class="flex flex-col md:flex-row bg-mustard-yellow xl:max-h-[32rem]">
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center px-5 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto md:ml-auto md:mr-16">
        <h2 class="uppercase text-medium-blue font-bold tracking-widest">
          Interested in flying?
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-5xl text-dark-blue font-bold leading-tight">
          Come try it out with an Intro Flight at High Tide Aviation
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 my-10">
          Flying can be daunting task; manning the controls even more so. If you
          want to see what itâ€™s like to be in the pilotâ€™s seat, come visit us
          for an introductory flight where weâ€™ll show you the ropes and see if
          flying is the right choice for you.
        </p>
        <a href="/intro-flight" class="btn-blue hover:bg-white">
          Request an Intro Flight
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1">
      <Image
        src={TopView}
        alt="View from the top of the airplane cockpit"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        quality={10}
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
